    <id>imageconverter</id>
    <name>Image Converter &amp; Resizer</name>
    <summary>Convert and resize images (HEIC/HEIF → JPEG)</summary>
    <description>
        <![CDATA[Right-click an image to convert or resize it. Currently supports converting HEIC/HEIF files to JPEG via Imagick.
        Needs imagemagick with HEIC support installed and the PHP Imagick extension enabled.]]>
